            "title": "建行亞洲推一站式養老金融服務",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國建設銀行（亞洲）推出一站式全面養老金融方案，建行亞洲客戶投保太平人壽合資格產品，積分可兌換太平養老社區入住資格，今日至6 月30日前投保首100名客戶可享灣區門診服務。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">此外，「貴賓理財」新客戶享 3 個月特惠定存年利率5.38厘，「智選理財」及一般個人銀行客戶透過「e 賬戶服務」開戶可享 1 個月特惠定存年利率 6.68厘。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"建行亞洲副行長陳麗明(左)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/WhatsApp-Image-2025-05-09-at-10.57.45-1.jpeg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"建行亞洲副行長陳麗明(左)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/WhatsApp-Image-2025-05-09-at-10.57.45-1.jpeg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">建行亞洲副行長陳麗明(左)</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">養老金融方案覆蓋了「老有所養、老有所居、老有所享、老有所醫、老有所樂」五個領域，除上述入住養老社區、門診服務外，也包括人壽儲蓄保險及延期年金計劃、保單逆按、安老按揭、跨境直聯匯款等，而憑藉建行信用卡，在港怡醫院體檢有折扣優惠。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1034x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/WhatsApp-Image-2025-05-09-at-10.57.45-2.jpeg.webp\">\n<img src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1034x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/WhatsApp-Image-2025-05-09-at-10.57.45-2.jpeg.webp\"/>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">另一方面，客戶投保太平人壽（香港）合資格產品，還可獲得高達23%的首年首次繳付保費折扣以及12500港元的現金獎賞。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14915027-%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e9%a4%8a%e8%80%81%e9%87%91%e8%9e%8d%e5%b8%82%e5%a0%b4%e8%bf%8e%e6%96%b0%e6%a9%9f%e9%81%87-%e5%bb%ba%e8%a1%8c%ef%bc%88%e4%ba%9e%e6%b4%b2%ef%bc%89%e4%b8%80%e7%ab%99%e5%bc%8f%e6%9c%8d",
